{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a2dbc86bcb","title":"和团干部的一次谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"14fce3c461","index":0,"year":1947,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"a2dbc86bcb"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8794b353f9","type":"paragraph","text":"和团干部的一次谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"a2dbc86bcb"},{"id":"84e692190d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年3月）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"a2dbc86bcb"},{"id":"2e8b1bae3f","type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石打位，是为了争地盘，占领延安，他好升会庆祝，我们就给他地盘。我们打仗是要仔房他的兵员，缴获他的装备，消灭他的有生力量，来壮大自己。这样，他打他的，我打我的好了。等蒋介石算清这笔账，后悔就退了","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"a2dbc86bcb"},{"id":"850af72e91","type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石占领延安，《双十协定》就被他彻底撕毁了，他将为全国人民所睡弃，我们撤出延安，意味着我们要解放西安，解放南京，解放全中国！这是战争的转折点","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"a2dbc86bcb"}],"page":{"id":"81fd7caca9","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"a2dbc86bcb","start":486,"end":486}}}},"__N_SSG":true}